items.comment: Really? This is one of the most talked up red ales in Oz. Bit old?
Perhaps. The packaged date has rubbed off the can, of course. It's ok, but by my taste the tropical fruit hops clash with the caramel.
We've been drinking off and on all day, so my palate might be off.
Ah, day drinking. Is there anything better? :)
